The paper discusses the Cooperative Patent Classifications (CPC) and provides statistical analysis and mapping of patent portfolios. This involves information retrieval (IR) techniques for mapping and analysis, as well as machine learning (LG) for constructing statistical models. The paper also touches on cybersecurity (CY) concerns related to patent portfolios. Finally, the paper provides online tools for data visualization and analysis, which could fall under digital libraries (DL) and social informatics (SI).
